
# BC Eats Project
Repository to upload the BC Eats project.

## About
Website for a fake company (food delivery service) in BC, Canada.

* Initial idea
    * Single page with several sections to promote the company and its services.

* Improvements
    * Added responsive web design.
	* Added a sticky navigation bar once the header gets passed.
	* Added effects to some 'call to action' buttons.
	* Added animations that gets triggered on scroll.

## Screenshot
![](https://github.com/jemtca/BC-Eats/blob/master/screenshots/bceats.gif)

## Technologies Used
* HTML, CSS, JavaScript.
* CSS boost: [Normalize](https://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/), [Responsive Grid System](http://www.responsivegridsystem.com/), [Animate](https://daneden.github.io/animate.css/).
* Frameworks: [Ionicons](https://ionicons.com/).
* jsDelivr: [respond](https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/respond.js), [HTML5Shiv](https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/html5shiv), [selectivizr](https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/selectivizr).
* JavaScript libraries: [jQuery](https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/jquery), [Waypoints](https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/waypoints).
* Cloud service: [GitHub Pages](https://pages.github.com/).
